I have been meaning to write these past weeks, but every time I sit
down, words seem so inadequate. The deep sadness which accompanies the
profound love we shared remains undiminished throughout all this time.
The measure of the depth that it is.

Sivananda and Joan will be spreading Her ashes by the lake at the ashram
