sending me exotic snaps of their joyous times together. Patricia and
I mused of the day that would come when we could travel together.
Iceland was one of the darts on our map. Looking at my kids snaps.. they
are missing Her smile planted in the image. They also have some of
Patricia's ashes with them for some special found location. She is
finally getting around.

No worries about the scans. You can add them to collection of digital
snaps next time you come down -- I guess summer holidays for the boys
